sequence-diagram

Admin [icon: shield, color: red]
Frontend [icon: monitor, color: gray]
Backend [icon: server, color: blue]
Provider [icon: briefcase, color: teal]
User [icon: user, color: blue]
PaymentGateway [icon: credit-card, color: green]
Database [icon: database, color: purple]

%% ------------------------------
%% ADMIN LOGIN
%% ------------------------------

Admin > Frontend: Login Request
Frontend > Backend: Validate Admin Credentials
activate Backend
Backend --> Frontend: JWT + Dashboard Access Granted
deactivate Backend

%% ------------------------------
%% REVIEW PROVIDER REGISTRATIONS
%% ------------------------------

Admin > Frontend: View Pending Provider Applications
Frontend > Backend: Fetch Pending Providers
Backend > Database: Query Pending Provider Docs
Database --> Backend: Provider List
Backend --> Frontend: Send Provider Applications

Admin > Frontend: Approve/Reject Provider
Frontend > Backend: Update Provider Status
Backend > Database: Update Provider Record

alt Provider Approved
Backend > PaymentGateway: Trigger Registration Fee Payment
PaymentGateway --> Backend: Payment Status
Backend --> Provider: Approval + Payment Confirmation
else Provider Rejected
Backend --> Provider: Rejection Notification
end

%% ------------------------------
%% MONITOR SERVICE REQUESTS
%% ------------------------------

Admin > Frontend: View All Active Orders
Frontend > Backend: Request Orders Data
Backend > Database: Fetch Active Orders
Database --> Backend: Orders Data
Backend --> Frontend: Display Orders

%% ------------------------------
%% HANDLE DISPUTES (USER â†” PROVIDER)
%% ------------------------------

User > Backend: File Dispute
Backend --> Admin: Dispute Notification

Admin > Frontend: Review Dispute
Frontend > Backend: Request Dispute Details
Backend > Database: Fetch Dispute Info
Database --> Backend: Dispute Details

Admin > Backend: Resolve Dispute (Refund / Reassign / Warn Provider)
Backend > Database: Update Dispute + Order Status
Backend --> User: Resolution Notification
Backend --> Provider: Resolution Notification

%% ------------------------------
%% COMMISSION & PAYOUT MANAGEMENT
%% ------------------------------

Admin > Frontend: View Commission Reports
Frontend > Backend: Request Commission Data
Backend > Database: Fetch Payments + Commissions
Database --> Backend: Data Returned
Backend --> Frontend: Display Report

Admin > Backend: Approve Vendor Payout
Backend > PaymentGateway: Transfer Amount to Provider
PaymentGateway --> Backend: Confirmation
Backend --> Provider: Payout Completed Notification

%% ------------------------------
%% MANAGE NOTIFICATIONS
%% ------------------------------

Admin > Backend: Send Platform Announcement
Backend --> User: Broadcast Notification
Backend --> Provider: Broadcast Notification
